# Biblia Studio

Follow **`AGENTS.md`** (repo root) first.

- **Packages:** `docs/02-package-map.md` — `@biblia-studio/*` vs `apps/*`.
- **Apps:** Hexagonal — `docs/05-hexagonal-apps.md`; UI as driving adapters only.
- **UI:** `docs/04-ui-philosophy.md` — lifeless / skinless / headless / boneless.
- **Upstream:** Door43 / formats — link [uW-Tools-Collab](https://github.com/unfoldingWord/uW-Tools-Collab); do not duplicate long spec prose.
- **Workflow:** `docs/06-ai-and-human-workflow.md` — human review expectations.
- **GitHub MCP:** `.cursor/mcp.json` + env `GITHUB_MCP_PAT` — see `docs/07-github-mcp.md`.
- **GitHub workflow:** `docs/08-github-agent-workflow.md` — issue → branch → push → draft PR (MCP); humans merge.
- **CI:** `.github/workflows/ci.yml` — same as local `lint` / `check-types` / `build`; PRs should pass.
- **First feature:** `docs/10-first-project.md` — CI on GitHub + branch protection + labels before big planning.

**Non-negotiables:** No secrets in code; minimal diffs; run `bun run lint` and `bun run check-types` before finishing; new deps need justification.
